place_description: Your Neighborhood Coffee and Ice Cream shop. Serving Hot and Iced Coffee, 24 flavors of Herseys Ice Cream. Milkshakes, fresh bakery

reviews_data.review_text: Owners were so nice and the atmosphere is very fun! I hope to return soon!
ordered a doordash from here and although they were out of what I wanted, the lady here was quick to call with a substitute that was just as delicious! Loved the coffee as well.
This is my favorite local coffee/ice cream shop. Huge portions, good prices, and everything is delicious!
Hours are not as posted on Google. Was closed at 6:30 pm on a Wednesday.
Catarina was absolutely amazing!!!!! She was kind and welcoming and made great suggestions.  10/10!!!! I will definitely be retrying!!!!
They've got Hershey's ice cream here!  Very friendly and welcoming. A nice variety of eats and treats. Highly recommend.

It is a cute little spot in a strip, I got multiple desserts for my Aunt's birthday and she loved the butter pound cake with strawberries   The owner was very  sweet and helpful!  All the desserts are homemade.  Will definitely take other who are dessert lovers!

The woman working was so sweet and super accommodating. She's so kind when she comes to serve you at your table and check on you. Croissants were amazing and the tea was awesome! Definitely worth checking out, my coworker had an amazing looking coffee milkshake!
Highly recommend! They also have authentic Colombian empanadas. The service is great too.
We always come here to have great ice cream and relax. An adorable place like home. Recommended!
Excellent ice cream and coffee. Even better service.
"Man". I have never taste this caramel bourbon ice cream coffee this drink was better than Casamigo forreal I don't drink alcohol no more this is my go too
Love going here with the family. So tasty and our whole family can easily share one sundae

Had the best cappuccino and banana split of my life here tonight. This is a great place, highly recommended it! Carolina was great 

*Update*

Went back with the family on Wednesday (2/28/24) and I have to say nothing changed, the banana split is still to die for, and the cappuccino is the best one I had! Carolina was awesome as always!
Nice place and good food
The other was so sweet and helpful. The ice cream was delicious. I ended up getting a coffee shake, so good! Definitely give it a try.

I came for a coffee at around 7pm and asked the server: is the coffee fresh? She confidently replied, yes. I asked her again, is the coffee, hot? She again replied with confidence, yes. Then I asked her, when did you brew the coffee, she said in the morning. Then I told her, how can your coffee be fresh and hot at 7pm if you brewed it in the morning. She replied, she can't, brew fresh coffee for me. Anyway, I purchased a Latte, but that doesn't taste good either- no taste of coffee in it.
My kids and I love this ice cream and coffee shop. It's cozy, the staff is friendly, and the desserts are fabulous!

Great prices! I got a latte, an empanada, and a croissant for $11. The quality is way better than Starbucks and the cost way lower. Selection (for coffee) is more limited because it is a more local establishment, but it is very charming. They served my coffee in a mug and it feels like a family owns and runs the shop together. Some games to play and cute little seating areas.

I definitely will be back to try the ice cream if I am ever in the area again!

Very impressed with the menu. I got a latte, pound cake, and empanadas.
Every item was the star of the show. This will be my regular stop when I'm in Concord.

Super cute family owned business. Have been multiple times and always received the best service. The inside is beautifully decorated with drawings of ice cream and coffee. They serve a variety of coffees, ice cream, milkshakes, banana splits and pastries. It is a cozy environment with different areas to choose from to sit and enjoy time with friends, family, or even by yourself. The staff is personable and always ready to help.
Love this coffee shop, tried it on DoorDash and I can't stop ordering from there, the red velvet cookies are a must try and the frappes are excellent, I would be visiting in person soon

NYC coffee snob here. They make one of the best Lattes in the area. It's not bitter like most other local places are. Wish I'd have found them earlier. Staff are pretty competent and efficient. They  get your order to you fairly fast even if you just walk in and order.
If they step up their bagel game and offer a bit more hot choices on their breakfast menu that would really propel them to a top spot.
I've still to find a place that'll fry an actual egg and serve it to you on a fresh roll. Everyone down here uses the prepackaged fake eggs and rubbery
Lenders  type bagels.
Pretty good parking but be aware some store side spots are reserved for the other businesses in the strip.
Amazing coffee and service!
Awesome
Awesome place... will definely be back
Great customer service. The Chai latte, beef empanadas, chicken empanada, pandeyuca were all delicious
Went there with the family thi morning for ice cream and a coffee. Great customer service, great selections, will definitely shop there again.
Very nice place, Coffee is some of the best ive had. I usually get their frappes.
Yummy!  Great customer service !
Love this place! Great for hand dipped ice cream and they have such an assortment, affordable as well. Would recommend to anyone, the service is always amazing and very friendly!
Amazing place, good coffee, fresh bakeries and very friendly staff
The best ice cream in Concord, North Carolina.
delicious
One of the hidden gems of concord. The speciality milkshakes are awesome. Always great customer service.

THEEEEE BEST!!!! We found this place pretty spur of the moment and we're Obsessed! We couldn't decide among so many AMAZING options !! I got the salted pretzel coffee shake!!! DEVINE!! The ice cream is phenomenal and the coffee is top tier! My boyfriend got the chocolate chip brownie with mint chocolate chip ice cream and LOVED IT!! Definitely recommend this place for a sweet treat! The staff is super nice and friendly! We tried a few ice creams and loved them all of course lol

Do yourself a favor and try this place! Coffee rivals Starbucks, atmosphere is cozy, empanadas are excellent and ice cream flavors are complex. Milkshakes are over the top...literally! Love the owner, you must try!!
Our grandson dropped his whole cup of ice cream upside down on the floor and the lady gave him another one immediately.
It's pricey
Nice place, good ice cream

We just moved to Concord five months ago and we enjoy coffee and ice cream. We just happened to stop in and have been returning ever since. The coffee is top notch hot or iced. This is a family owned and run business and they could not be more gracious! The baked goods are homemade and the owner offers catering as well. The consistency is what matters, and there goods and services are just that. I hope this quaint and excellent shop will continue to grow and have favor in the community!

We decided to get some ice cream on a whim one Sat. After doing a quick Google search in the area, Coffee and Cream popped up so we decided to give it a try. Needless to say, we were pleasantly surprised at how delicious the Hershey's -branded ice cream was! There were over 20 flavors and each was amazing (I highly recommend the Key Lime Pie ice cream). More importantly, the staff was very friendly and let us try multiple samples.

We highly recommend giving this place a try if you're in the Concord/Harrisburg area!
Absolutely amazing. We are in town from Kansas City and found this on Google. Stopped in and found a hidden secret. Absolutely wonderful drinks and food. Will be back to try the ice cream.

Very kind staff and clean cafe. There are many options to choose from including coffee, pastries, and ice cream. The iced latte I ordered was so delicious, it reminded me of the coffee I was accustomed to drinking back in my home in New Zealand. I highly recommend giving this coffee shop a try!
Great place to go for ice cream
What a delightful shop!  I will return!

This is an amazing place, a hidden gem of the Charlotte/Concord area. The girls who serve are super friendly and amazing, the food is delicious and the atmosphere is super cozy. If you are in the area, I recommend you visit this place.

Este es un increible lugar, una gema escondida del area de Charlotte/Concord. Las chicas que atienden son super amables e increibles, la comida deliciosa y el ambiente es super acogedor. Si estan por el area, les recomiendo que visiten este lugar
Awesome spot for coffee & ice cream family owned! Had a French Vanilla Latte it was really good. Definitely come check them out.
Very kind and considerate staff.  Chai milkshake was good, sweet and creamy but missed the spices a bit.  Looking forward to trying more things.

This little shop looks unassuming from outside, but boy, does it pack a punch!! It was about 10 minutes before closing time, and we decided to grab some dessert  to go; at the same time, support a small local business. Wow, were we impressed. The customer service is TOP TIER. The inside is very eclectic, and the shop owner will tell you about the history of each piece in the store. The ice cream flavors are very unique and so amazingly delicious.  The price is excellent, and I can't wait to go back and try something else. This place just celebrated a 2 year anniversary, and I hope to see it around for decades to come. I can promise you that you won't regret stopping in for a scoop (or 3)!
Ow wee!!! If I could give 10 stars I would this is a must try the service I  received walking in the door was nothing less then amazing   my new favorite spot and should be yours.   Highly recommend
The owner was very pleasant and made me a dirty chai blended like a frap. The inside is clean and the drink hit the spot. Would go here again.
Really cute, small, and cozy family owned coffee shop. The servers were very attentive to customer needs.
I always like the coffee as they have many flavors to try from.
Best customer service I've experienced in a long time; delicious milkshake and really cute space to hang out.

I tried this coffee place for the first time a couple of days ago. The capuccino was superb as well as freshly baked biscuits with chocolate chips. Good for in place or take away. Easy access with parking facilities. Cozy and friendly place. I'll be back and try other options that look great. Strongly recommended
Amazing ice cream and shakes. Definitely recommend to others!

This is a lively and lovely shop with delicious hand made pastries. It feels welcoming and the drinks are top notch too. I highly recommend the coffee shake with any chocolate oriented ice cream, it comes with a shot of expresso so it really provides a rich flavor to the drink. The chocolate filled croissant is warm and is an amazing side to any cold drink you can order. The caramel frappe is also irresistible. Can't wait to come again.
Sells old bakery items. Please avoid purchasing the bakery goods. Disappointed in customer service.
Excellent experience. I had one of the Coffee-shakes and I would highly recommend it!

The smell when you walk-in is the truth! This place is wonderful. The ice cream and baked goods, specifically the red velvet cookie, are nothing short of amazing. The staff is always upbeat and friendly. I support them more than I need too
delicious and great customer service! the staff was so friendly
The BEST coffee in town and awesome customer service.
I LOVE this ice cream shop! They have so many options and they are all so good. I visit every time I am in the area.
Love this place...

Really good coffee and cake.
Owner make you feel welcome and the environment is really chill. Define stop by and get something.
We absolutely love the local ice cream spot. This coffee ice cream drink is to die for and they have empanadas! Everything has always been yummy, we highly recommend it!
The croissants weren't bad but they had a weird taste like they used an ingredient you wouldn't normally use but my chocolate milkshake was delicious.

Only had a few minutes...they were all smiles, offered to clean my reusable mug, made vegan substitutions (with their vegan ice cream) and clearly frothed everything up with a love for what they do. Outdoor and indoor seating to enjoy your shakes, smoothies, pastries and of course coffee drinks.

Happened upon this charm during our vacation to Concord. Ended up going twice during our 3 day trip. Couldn't decide if we were drawn more to the incredibly sweet owner or the amazing yum yums!! Have a coffee shake and a pastry...you will not regret one calorie.

My family and I go to this business often.  The family who owns is absolutely amazing!!! They are so friendly and helpful! Their drinks and shakes look like art!!
Gorgeous environment!

I wish I could give 10 stars!!!

First time I visited was on the weekend- got a cappuccino and it was great! Today, I woke up and thought- a cappuccino would be awesome. So, at 8:00 I went about to the coffee shop. They aren't open till 10am- what? With a drive through coffee house opening up just 300 feet away? Why would you not have your shop open when humans actually drink coffee?? I guess they can still get ice cream at 10am- IDK.  The cappuccino was good, but they lost my business today. How do you have a coffee shop that opens at 10am???
Good coffee, bad business!
Great ice cream and very friendly folks. Make you feel at home.
Great coffee and lovely staff

I'm so happy that this place is so close to home! Wish I've found them out sooner! The family who owns this place are such sweet & wonderful people. The place is spacious, welcoming, clean & warm. I love their ice cream choices & menu. Definitely my family's go to place now for ice cream! May God bless your family & business!

Absolutly amazing service. Came in not knowing what I might like and they reccomended something absolutly delicious! Couldn't help but eat it a bit before taking the picture, that's how good! Only cafe I'll be attending for now on
Nice spot, great ice cream but definitely needs music for atmosphere!
Icecream coffee shake is yum!

This is a sweet little coffee and ice cream shop. The employees when I went (who I think we're most likely the owners) were very friendly and accommodating. It was nice that we had our ice cream in a glass ice cream bowl. It was a nice little touch that made it a little more special. Many flavors of Hershey's Ice Cream and they were happy to let you try samples. Look forward to going back and trying a milkshake!
Best coffee and ice cream If you're looking for good ice cream or even a coffee milkshake this is the place to go friendly environment clean store and the richest ice cream ever

I went in for the first time yesterday, and I'm mad I didn't know about this place sooner. The woman working was super nice and very patient while I was figuring out what I wanted, and have excellent advice. The coffee shake is amazing. This is definitely my go to spot now for anything Coffee or ice cream!
I've been here in person twice and ordered off DD twice. This place is a must try. Locally owned by an incredibly nice family.
Best coffee and ice cream in Concord and surrounding! It's a must try! It's a family own cafe and the owners are super super kind! Totally recommended!
Great coffee, ton of choices for ice cream.  Owners were very friendly and helpful.  Great atmosphere.  We will definitely be back!
So good.
Fantastic coffee and pastries. The service was great. Will be going back.

Amazing experience!Their  espresso is to die for, just like Italy. It's very very rare to find cafes that know how to make true italian espresso and this is the one! The icecream was delicious as well, definitely a must try!
A great gem. A ton of flavors of ice cream. Awesome atmosphere. Great price
Delicioso/ Delicious !!!

1st time here. Good icecream, good cookies, good pastries, good coffee. Great customer service. They make you feel welcome, and sometimes, businesses forget that very important part. Thank you for making me feel like I'm the most important customer you have.

The staff is incredibly kind! On my first visit, I was given a detailed overview of everything available and I can tell that they really care about their customers' happiness. They work to provide drinks and treats that are suitable to a variety of needs, whether it be dietary restrictions or flavor preferences. The ice cream, pastries, and coffee are all delicious and they offer plenty to try. I even took my grandma to visit-- she tends to be somewhat picky and critical, and she also enjoyed. I love this shop and I fully recommend!
Muy rico un muy bue servicio

This place was wonderful! The girls behind the counter were super sweet and helpful! We loved our milkshakes and their baked goods were also fantastic. We will definitely be coming back and I'm excited to try the coffee!
Coffe shake was amazing! Mixed it with the Butter bourbon ice cream !! 6
Hands down the BEST "coffee milk shake" I've had! The customer service was amazing !!!! Do yourself a favor, try the butter bourbon caramel truffle espresso shake! Whew ! Deeee-licious
The Vanilla lattes are amazing here! The owner is super friendly and kind, family owned.  Overall a Great place!
Amazing. Great ice cream! Great coffee! Even better people.
This place is AMAZING! My girls love the many flavors of ice cream and I LOVED the ice Carmel latte! So yummy!
Hot chocolate was so good
Really great coffee shop! I would take this over Starbucks any day. Custom options for coffee, ice cream and milkshakes. Very unique

This was our first time visiting this shop. The place is amazing and so are the people. They are very friendly and welcoming.  We only tried their icecream and it was excellent.  The portions are great for the price. The shop is nice and clean as well. Will definitely be going back and I highly recommend them.
This place was amazing in all ways. The cashiers were very welcoming and friendly, along with that there ice cream was amazing. Over all I give this place 5stars :)
Excellent coffee and excellent ice cream!!
My favorite coffee place :) the owners are so friendly and everything here is so good! This is my new favorite place to hangout and work on my computer
Absolutely great drinks you can tell are made with love.  Super nice family running this place!

Es un lugar super acogedor
Su exelente preparacion   de cafe y
Su variedad  de helados
the best service the best ice cream the best coffee from different countries and also gourmet coffee they made me feel at home I definitely have to go back

I would definitely not get coffee here. I can not speak on the ice cream (which is just Hershey's), but the coffee tasted like CARDBOARD. I have had plenty of coffee from plenty of different places none have ever been this awful. None of the prices are listed for the coffee, and there's poor organization. What I mean by this is three different people helped me and then did not even charge me for the right size drink. I asked them 3 different times if they had a Frappuccino's and they insisted they did. They also were confusing a hot drink for a cold drink. When I received my drink it did not contain ice at all. This coffee was extremely overpriced for something that I could not even consume. $10 for a coffee drink floors me
Delicious ! Friendly staff
Great family friendly place. ICE cream is delicious

It was my first time visiting the location, and I thoroughly enjoyed it. My wife had a Rum Raisin milkshake, and I had a Cookies and Cream milkshake, both of which were delicious. I'll definitely be back because I enjoy the atmosphere inside that small establishment.
Great iced coffee.  I take mine black no additives. The coffee was smooth and not bitter. Also purchased a brownie with nuts. Great taste,  not too sweet.
The Sea Salted Caramel Cookies & Cream ice cream is to die for!! Everyone was very sweet and they had affordable prices. Will definitely come back!
Outstanding customer service, good vibe about the place. Amazing dessert! First time, I will be coming back and I recommend them.

This place was ABSOLUTELY INCREDIBLE! I have never had such an amazing customer service experience in my life! Everything was completely explained and we were helped tremendously with all the amazing ice cream options! This place is seriously the best and I can't wait to go back! The menu options are endless and are all so fabulous!

This place is outstanding. They have a ton of ice cream flavors. I got the coffee toffee something and it was a rich coffee ice cream with fudge and toffee bits. Heavenly. We got 4 big cups of ice cream and a blonde for only 19.00. They have other baked goods too and pops. And they have a full line of coffees too. I think this is my new happy place. You must check it out.

Listen up coffee lovers and those aversive to it,

As self defined coffee aficionados, My cousin and I had some of the best coffee we've ever tasted, iced and hot! The manager was so kind, so don't be afraid to try out this place. if it's your first time--she explains everything offered. There's plenty of tables to converse with pals (or lovers ) over coffee, milkshake, pastries, empanadas, and so much more. And, an air hockey table if you're looking for a friendly battle while waiting for your order. Overall a welcoming and comfortable environment no matter the occasion (school work, meetings, etc.) to indulge in some delicious treats!
Best milk shake I've had in a long time.  I could actually use my straw for it.  They can make any flavor of ice cream into a milk shake. The owner and family were so nice.

Great ice cream, milkshakes and treats! This has got to be one of the best ice cream shops in the area. I would like to see them figure out how to market their coffee drinks better. While it seems like they're willing to make any coffee style drink, their menu doesn't describe or offer much... This could really be a big selling point as there aren't many locally owned coffee shops, especially in a high traffic area like this one.
This place is great! Super cute on the inside and the coffee was so yummy. The staff was so friendly and they had literally anything I could ask for. 10/0
This place was awesome. They custom made a waffle bowl with ice cream, whipped cream, and strawberries on top! It was great. We will definitely be back.

Family went for ice cream. Kids enjoyed it though one didn't care for the superman ice cream, but ate it all. Our other son had the mystical mermaid. It was good as I tried a bite. My wife and I had two toffee ice reams that were good. Hot fudge on my older sons cone, not so good. We will be back but not get an ice cream cone with hot fudge and sprinkles again.

ABSOLUTELY LOVE THIS PLACE!

The people are super nice and the attention is like no other! It's a very peaceful place to hang out and get some ice cream or a cup of coffee if that's what you prefer. Lots of flavors and popsicles to choose from.

I PROMISE L I'LL BE BACK! Thank you!
Went here with my 2 toddlers. Service was amazing. Very nice people. Ice cream was delicious!! Definitely will be back. Also a coffee shop. Can't wait to try the coffee from Columbia!!

I stumbled upon this place while waiting on my car to be serviced. The ice cream shop was clean and had plenty of seating for you to social distance. The young lady behind the counter was super pleasant and helped me decide what kind of ice cream I should get. When she told me they make their waffle cones IN HOUSE I was even more excited. For those of you who want a sugar free option, the butter pecan is DELICIOUS. I had an opportunity to meet and chat with the owner, who was equally as pleasant and welcoming as his employee. I recommend this place and I look forward to grabbing more sweet treats from Coffee and Cream again in the near future! Oh, and the process were EXTREMELY reasonable!
Was looking for a good ice cream place and decided to try Coffee and Cream, was very impressed with the flavor variety! Good ice cream and friendly staff! We will definitely be back.
Our first time in and we thoroughly enjoyed the staff and the ice cream. We have been looking for a place that serves old fashioned hard ice cream so now we found our "go to" shop.
Awesome place, great ice cream and great prices! Highly recommended!
